    <h2 {...{
      "id": "tutorial"
    }}>{`Tutorial`}</h2>
    <Steps headingDepth={3} mdxType="Steps">
      <ol>
        <li>
          <h3 {...{
            "id": "install-vector"
          }}>{`Install Vector`}</h3>
          <p>{`If you haven't already, install Vector. Here's a script for the lazy:`}</p>
          <InstallationCommand mdxType="InstallationCommand" />
          <p>{`Or `}<a parentName="p" {...{
              "href": "/docs/setup/installation/"
            }}>{`choose your preferred installation method`}</a>{`.`}</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 {...{
            "id": "configure-it"
          }}>{`Configure it`}</h3>
          <p>{`Vector runs with a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
              "href": "/docs/setup/configuration/"
            }}>{`configuration file`}</a>{` that tells it which
`}<a parentName="p" {...{
              "href": "/components/"
            }}>{`components`}</a>{` to run and how they should interact. Let's create
one that simply pipes a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
