              <li parentName="ul">{`The `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`vector...`}</inlineCode>{` command starts Vector with our previously created config file.`}</li>
            </ul>
          </CodeExplanation>
          <p>{`Your input event will get echoed back (along with some service logs) unchanged:`}</p>
          <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
              "className": "language-text"
            }}>{`... some logs ...
Hello World!
`}</code></pre>
          <p>{`That's because the raw input text of our source was captured internally within
the field `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`message`}</inlineCode>{`, and the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`text`}</inlineCode>{` `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`encoding.codec`}</inlineCode>{` option of our sink prints
the raw contents of `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`message`}</inlineCode>{` only.`}</p>
          <Alert type="info" mdxType="Alert">
